snippet.title: DHAR MANN Gives SHAMED DANCER Her Big Break *Emotional* ft/ Matt Steffanina
snippet.description:
Lizzy Howell has been shamed for her size her entire life, and she desperately wants to move to Los Angeles to pursue her dreams. I have 48 hours to make that happen! Dhar Mann offers her a huge opportunity, but can she overcome her fears to take advantage of the biggest break of her life? 

GoFundMe to help Lizzy pursue her dreams: https://www.gofundme.com/f/help-lizzy-move-to-la

See Lizzy's incredible acting performance on Dhar's channel: Ballerina FAT SHAMED By Dancer ft. @Jordan Matter and Lizzy Howell | Dhar Mann https://youtu.be/9skk3hIZq98
